        this contradiction to maintain a coherent understanding of Event X.'
      expected_behavior: The agent invokes RECONCILE_HARMONY. It analyzes metadata (e.g., source reliability, contextual fit,
        temporal proximity to other confirmed events) and applies the 'least_disruptive' policy, perhaps inferring a sub-event
